# USER.md — User Profiles & Permissions

> Maps Slack user IDs to roles, permissions, and preferences.
> The orchestrator references this file to personalize responses and enforce access control.

---

## Roles

| Role | Description | Access Level |
|---|---|---|
| `admin` | Firm owner / IT admin. Full access to all agents and tools. | Full |
| `attorney` | Licensed attorney. Can trigger workflows, access case data. | Standard |
| `paralegal` | Paralegal / legal assistant. Can search and trigger limited workflows. | Standard |
| `staff` | Office staff. Read-only access, basic queries only. | Limited |

---

